<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge" />
    <title>verification code</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f7;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        color: #51545e;
        width: 100%;
      }
      table {
        border-spacing: 0;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        width: 100%;
      }
      .email-container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        text-align: center; /* Ensures content is centered */
      }
      .email-header {
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: white;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .email-header img {
        max-width: 100px;
      }
      .email-body {
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center; /* Ensures body text is centered */
      }
      .email-footer {
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f4f4f7;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #a8aaaf;
      }
      .verification-code {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: white;
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: bold;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .email-body {
          padding: 10px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <center>
      <table class="email-container" align="center">
        <!-- Header -->
        <tr>
          <td class="email-header">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100x50?text=Company+Logo" alt="Company Logo" />
            <h1>code de vérification</h1>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- Body -->
        <tr>
          <td class="email-body">
            <p>bonjour,</p>
            <p>Nous avons reçu une demande pour vérifier votre adresse e-mail.</p>
            <p>Votre code de vérification est</p>

            <!-- Verification Code -->
            <p class="verification-code">{{ verificationCode }}</p>

            <p>Si vous n'avez pas demandé ce code, vous pouvez ignorer cet email.</p>
            <p>Merci<br />LOUSA</p>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <tr>
          <td class="email-footer">
            <p>Vous recevez cet e-mail car vous avez demandé un code de vérification sur notre site.</p>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </center>
  </body>
</html>
